subject.value: Workforce to EC Payroll - Time: System Details not maintained

body.value:
Dear Administrator,

The execution of the WFS Inbound process run on ${date:now:yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss}  failed to execute as the system details have not been maintained in the extensions. Please do maintain them and then execute the process.

Regards,
3rd Party Integration Team

subject.value: Workforce to EC Payroll - Time: Invalid Files

body.value:
Dear Administrator,

PFA the exceptions were caught during execution of the WFS Inbound process run on 
${date:now:yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss} .

wrapContent.value:
Dear Administrator, The following exceptions were caught during execution of the process. Note the following details.

File Name Directory Exception Message
${property.INBOUND_FILENAME} ${property.INBOUND_FILE_REMOTE_DIRECTORY} ${exception.message}

wrapContent.value:
Dear Administrator,

The process failed to execute as the system details have not been maintained in the extensions. Please do maintain them and then execute the process.

Dear Administrator, The Transmission for the following files was attempted. These files were dropped from processing as the data seems to be incorrect. Kindly check the data and replace the file in the mentioned SFTP location for re-processing.

File Name SFTP Location
${property.INBOUND_FILENAME} ${property.INBOUND_FILE_REMOTE_DIRECTORY}

Dear Administrator, The Transmission for the following files was attempted. Please note the details below. The IDOC Number is available for successful transmissions and will be blank for error cases/non-transmission files.
